<li><font color="#e00000"><strong>SECURITY FIX: A race condition exists in the <a href="http://man.openbsd.org/?query=pppd&amp;sektion=8">pppd(8)</a> daemon which may cause it to alter the file permissions of an arbitrary file.</strong></font><br>
    <a href="errata31.html#pppd">A source code patch is available</a>.<br>
    <a href="stable.html"><font color="#00b000">[Applied to stable]</font></a>
