<li>Add volatile to sig_atomic_t. Stand well back.
<li>Use rasops instead of rcons in <a href="http://man.openbsd.org/?query=cgthree&amp;sektion=4&amp;arch=sparc">cgthree(4/SPARC)</a> and <a href="http://man.openbsd.org/?query=cgsix&amp;sektion=4&amp;arch=sparc">cgsix(4/SPARC)</a>.
