a138 3
<li>Make <a href="http://man.openbsd.org?query=newsyslog&amp;sektion=8">newsyslog(8)</a> actually run the command it's asked to run. Also, add new interpretation of a null command.
<li>Fix <a href="http://man.openbsd.org?query=newsyslog&amp;sektion=8">newsyslog(8)</a>'s handling of empty lines.
