<li>The search for a shorter rulebase continues, <a href="http://www.openbsd.org/cgi-bin/man.cgi?query=pf&amp;sektion=4">pf(4)</a> now recognises 'self' as an address, meaning all IPv4 and IPv6 addresses on all interfaces. 
