<li><a href="http://www.openbsd.org/cgi-bin/man.cgi?query=ps&amp;sektion=1">ps(1)</a> shows flag 'x' for <a href="http://www.openbsd.org/cgi-bin/man.cgi?query=systrace&amp;sektion=4">systrace(4)</a>'d processes.
