<li><font color="#e00000"><strong>SECURITY FIX: fix a buffer overflow in AFS/Kerberos token handling in <a href="http://www.openbsd.org/cgi-bin/man.cgi?query=sshd&amp;sektion=8">sshd(8)</a>, and send a complete ticket.</strong></font><br>
